{"tid":491413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人知聯和墟個羅婆婆仲健唔健在？","createTime":"2017-12-06T13:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T08:47:01.000Z","uid":148884,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b502085798dc66a5a3ea42e1bb5b7930b604c88f","tid":491413,"uid":148884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:22:34.000Z","msg":"頭先無意中禁咗入去一兩年前嘅報導<br />\n因為唔係住個頭<br />\n想知有無人知婆婆近況？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/06/211541_5fe84d3d7f89f9857c83acdb42e6ff47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F211541_5fe84d3d7f89f9857c83acdb42e6ff47.jpg&h=2de73cca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/06/211542_7e03db075937d4f19c687207bbf8e03a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F211542_7e03db075937d4f19c687207bbf8e03a.jpg&h=161d9945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋今日天氣開始凍<br />\n真心好希望大家多d關心街上面嘅老人家<br />\n有多餘錢嘅買小小食物關心下佢地<br />\n有時見到香港街邊老人家真係好心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己都會買少少野問候下佢哋，聽下佢哋嘅故事<br />\n<br />\n或者大家有無留意到d老人家好需要幫忙<br />\n/點幫到佢哋<br />\n歡迎大家討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想社會多少少溫暖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff3b229fa5aba46bfe4603aeaa36bbe6fb781b4","tid":491413,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"婆婆咁老仲做砵仔糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bc5ce7885a5b2c2f7009379b013c7d16183b8f","tid":491413,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:27:27.000Z","msg":"佢冇擺好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e24574203a93f00991d3a239fa6427d13cd4c15","tid":491413,"uid":151338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:40:54.000Z","msg":"我都想知<br />\n推推"},{"pid":"b589b1bdd6ebb3dde8e2a62399806102520b9a14","tid":491413,"uid":148884,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:54:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Kq-KrbIA_GE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKq-KrbIA_GE&d=7SLwcdWVY8Mpy4yKxH5Fd54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=08b1790e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Kq-KrbIA_GE</a><br />\n仲有銅鑼灣個面粉公仔伯伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到佢哋d故事真係好心嗡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港仲有大把呢d俾仔女拋棄嘅老人家"},{"pid":"f9b7b2f3062973e0d429b4a55e0024ca21ed6619","tid":491413,"uid":148884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:54:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢冇擺好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n知唔知佢去咗邊？"},{"pid":"d45989565e2370dcbe667bdf23dd6c0a2a5e0e73","tid":491413,"uid":148884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>婆婆咁老仲做砵仔糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 成九十幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好勁"},{"pid":"979b4608e0c0ddb18b007d2887437ff39d3d865d","tid":491413,"uid":148884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:47:01.000Z","msg":"無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}